headline.main: Burmester Wins Maiden Title After Blowing Away Field
headline.print_headline: Burmester Wins Maiden Title After Blowing Away Field

lead_paragraph: Iran and neighboring Azerbaijan agreed on Sunday to work towards completing their portion of a planned freight railway route from Europe to South Asia, Iranian state media reported.
